title: Who is the most exceptional singer in One Direction?

og.title: Who is the most exceptional singer in One Direction?
og.description:
Answer (1 of 50): So, let me give you guy's actual answers, the most skilled, is Liam payne, Liam has great control, can seamlessly tap into his head and chest voice, he can even hit high notes without falsetto.

Harry Styles has a very deep voice and is really skilled, can hit amazing high notes...
